## Challenges & Solutions
1. Routing Errors on Page Refresh
Problem: /login and /signup returned 404 on refresh.
Solution: Implemented static.json redirect rules to route all traffic to index.html.
2. Deployment Build Failures
Problem: Missing config files and incorrect directory structure.
Solution: Corrected root directory, rebuilt project using Vite, and fixed missing tsconfig references.
3. Component Alignment Issues
Problem: Hero image and text alignment did not match Figma design.
Solution: Used Tailwind grid and flex utilities with controlled spacing and breakpoints.

## Future Improvements
Full Backend Integration
Connect login, signup, and dashboard to live authentication and database.
Order Management System
Clients can place, track, and review orders in real time.
Admin Dashboard
Writers and admins can manage users, orders, and services.
Payment Gateway Integration
Add Mpesa, PayPal, or Stripe for online payments.
